            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1673977577127-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a very generous drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil </strong>(enough to cover the base of the pan)</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated meat-free chick’n </strong>and cook for 6-7 min, turning halfway, or until crisp, golden and warmed through – these are your <strong>crispy fried chick'n pieces</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
