    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the<strong> </strong>meat-free chick’n<strong> </strong>is cooking, combine the <strong>mayo</strong> with 1/3 of the <strong>TABASCO® Sauce</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in a small bowl – this is your <strong>TABASCO® Sauce mayo</strong></p><p>Wash the <strong>gem lettuce</strong>,<strong> </strong>then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Remove 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> <strong>leaves</strong> from the <strong>gem lettuce</strong> and set aside, then cut the <strong>inner core<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into 4 <span class=\"text-danger\">[8]</span> wedges</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
